<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA95">
<l>eṉṉeñca mēyāṉeṉ ceṉṉiyāṉ ṟāṉavaṉai</l>
<l>vaṉṉeñcaṅ kīṇṭa maṇivaṇṇaṉ – muṉṉañcē</l>
<l>yūḻiyā ṉūḻi peyarttā ṉulakēttu</l>
<l>māḻiyā ṉattiyū rāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The inhabitant of my heart, the one in my head, he with sapphire colour</l>
<l>who had once torn [open] the strong heart of the Dhānava , he from a distant</l>
<l>aeon [is the one]  who puts the aeons into motion, the one with the discus</l>
<l>whom the world praises, whose village is Atti.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
